reviewText: anything from national geographic is excellent. this is no exception
This is an interesting fil with old footage that was in the archives of National Geographic magazine. Mostly still pictues with narrative. I was ok. 3 stars
The content is good but my dvds were scratched and skipped..

Amazing two NG DVD with few program on it. 125 years I thought there will be lots of materials to watch . I liked 'In search of Afghan Girl' and 'Titanic' all other materials also very enjoyable ! You can watch them together with your family!
I am amazed with all these NG programmes. You will never regret for bringing this DVD to your home!
Probably you will watch them again and again!
My love of history is enhanced through National Geographic: Best of 125 Years.  I appreciate and enjoy the colorful photos and insightful narratives.

If you love NG then theres no need to tell you how amazing these CD's are.  Now you have full screen detailed photography with so much detailed narrations.  Old and young, gotta love all the information.
